### AI Recommendations Endpoint Tests
### POST /api/aquariums/:aquariumId/recommendations
###
### Generates AI-powered recommendations for parameter deviations

### Test 1: Get recommendations for a parameter with deviation (Warning)
POST http://localhost:4321/api/aquariums/{{aquariumId}}/recommendations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parameter_id": "{{parameterId}}",
  "current_value": 8.5,
  "optimal_min": 7.8,
  "optimal_max": 8.3
}

